title: Ice Cube talks Fist Fight
itunes:title: Ice Cube talks Fist Fight
description:
N.O.R.E. & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this teaser of their sit down with Ice Cube the guys talk about Ice Cube's new film "Fist Fight" which hits theaters this weekend. Stay tuned for the full episode which covers NWA, the Friday film franchise, and a lot more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
